      <title>Viterra 交易愈发确定，惠誉上调邦吉评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/bunge-rating-raised-by-fitch-as-viterra-deal-looks-more-certain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级上调了邦吉全球公司的信用评级，将该农业公司进一步提升至投资级，因为其以 82 亿美元收购嘉能可支持的 Viterra 的交易看起来更加确定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/bunge-rating-raised-by-fitch-as-viterra-deal-looks-more-certain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 22:06:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
