    <item>
      <title>斯蒂芬·库里对 Under Armour 品牌的演变感到兴奋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-05/steph-curry-excited-about-under-armour-brand-evolution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[NBA 球星斯蒂芬·库里 (Steph Curry) 希望与创始人凯文·普朗克 (Kevin Plank) 一起重返 Under Armour。库里在彭博社纽约 Power Players 大会上表示：“我参与了设计、产品线的演变，我很高兴即使退役后也能继续从事这个事业。”(来源：彭博社)]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-05/steph-curry-excited-about-under-armour-brand-evolution</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 21:48:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
